/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n挑，次次都係人地外國平台發聲有撚用咩<br />\n夠膽你就係微博發文<br />\n<br />\n成篇野過濾完可能得返我們你們<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f03260da4de8ebad3bccad07e23e78682e83bc","tid":683910,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"其實佢開返間紀念館咪可以引香港人上去消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae2e4b27f65f533bd1ecfc82dd6c47582fd0eaa","tid":683910,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"來自iPhone 7 Plus?"},{"pid":"ace674f7f58703bebe657440eef9c7ae190ade79","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"販民班政棍事實係當六四學生政治資源喎"},{"pid":"764ea6cfc5281204f82b125ce4dadda25687a91b","tid":683910,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace674f7f58703bebe657440eef9c7ae190ade79","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"販民班政棍事實係當六四學生政治資源喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:24:49.000Z","msg":"環球時報總編輯講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a40e369d2b97c2e06281b5b24a7f3aec3601965","tid":683910,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"千方百計都要動搖共匪根基<br />\n不斷出賣共匪，科研人材益外國都唔益共匪"},{"pid":"4a31b3f58433f5e4fd6fae169f8cd7f714667088","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764ea6cfc5281204f82b125ce4dadda25687a91b","tid":683910,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace674f7f58703bebe657440eef9c7ae190ade79","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"販民班政棍事實係當六四學生政治資源喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018