9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764ea6cfc5281204f82b125ce4dadda25687a91b","tid":683910,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace674f7f58703bebe657440eef9c7ae190ade79","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:15:51.000Z","msg":"販民班政棍事實係當六四學生政治資源喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:24:49.000Z","msg":"環球時報總編輯講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"丁子霖當年都睇穿班友喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"丁子霖係不滿支聯會用「愛國」口號<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130601/18279474\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130601%2F18279474&d=5MiKebA02DEPhczAPv7l7Rv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=45d266ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130601%2F18279474&h=d3b38100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130601/18279474</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n而丁子霖晚上接受港台訪問時表示，對支聯會決定六四燭光集會當晚不用「愛國愛民」口號感滿意，認為是接納意見的表現，又希望支聯會集中精力辦好集會，這是對天安門母親最好的撫慰，呼籲將爭拗「放在一邊」，希望香港市民同樣以大局為重，放下有關「愛國」口號的爭議，出席六四燭光集會，令燭光較去年更多更亮。至於她會否接受辭去支聯會常委職務的徐漢光道歉，丁子霖則表示需再考慮。"},{"pid":"d079aed53e62c8a87d9699dfe4d0834d57b7c8f9","tid":683910,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6b0374d5c5e80ec7666a062c945aa104fe5b77","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1644488703704044eacb011b9b14350429dda6c5","tid":683910,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a31b3f58433f5e4fd6fae169f8cd7f714667088","tid":683910,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764ea6